    <string name="faq_header">Frequently Asked Questions</string>

    <string name="faq_q1">How do I upload a document?</string>
    <string name="faq_a1">On the Home screen, tap the \'+\' button or Upload icon. Then select a PDF file, enter a description, and tap \'Post Now\'.</string>

    <string name="faq_q2">What if I forgot my password?</string>
    <string name="faq_a2">On the Login screen, select \'Forgot Password?\'. The system will send you an email with instructions to reset it.</string>

    <string name="faq_q3">Why was my document rejected?</string>
    <string name="faq_a3">Documents may be rejected for copyright violations, inappropriate content, poor quality, or incorrect PDF format.</string>

    <string name="faq_q4">How do I report bad content?</string>
    <string name="faq_a4">In the document details, tap the \'...\' icon at the top and select \'Report Violation\'. We will review it within 24 hours.</string>

    <string name="faq_q5">Can I change my phone number?</string>
    <string name="faq_a5">Yes. Go to Settings -> Account Security -> Tap on Phone Number to update and verify via OTP.</string>

    <string name="faq_q6">Does StuShare charge fees?</string>
    <string name="faq_a6">Currently, StuShare is a free sharing platform for the student community.</string>

